<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>κυρίῳ μο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υ ἀδελφῷ Ὡρίων</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> 

    <lb n="2"/>Ἑρμείας. 

    <lb n="3"/>θαυμάζω εἴπερ ὁ ἀποστελλό-

    <lb n="4"/>μενος πρὸς σὲ τὸ πλοῖον 

    <lb n="5"/>τὸ τοῦ γεούχου καταλαμβάνει 

    <lb n="6"/>παρὰ σοί. πλὴν ἐὰν διὰ 

    <lb n="7"/><choice><corr>ἀμέλειαν</corr><sic>αμελιαν</sic></choice> τινὰ καταλάβῃ, 

    <lb n="8"/>σπούδασον πάραυτα τὸν 

    <lb n="9"/>ναύτην ἐπὶ τὴν <choice><corr>πόλιν</corr><sic>πολειν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="10"/>ἅμα τῷ πεμφθέντι συμμάχῳ 

    <lb n="11"/>ἐκπέμψαι. ἀλλ᾽<g type="mid punctus"/> ὅρα μὴ 

    <lb n="12"/>ἀμελήσῃς. <choice><corr>εἰ</corr><sic>η</sic></choice> καὶ εὐδία ἐστί 

    <lb n="13"/>καὶ τὸ πλοῖον <choice><corr>ἀνενέγκαι</corr><sic>ανενεγκε</sic></choice> οὐ 

    <lb n="14"/>δύναται ἐν τῇ σήμερον, 

    <lb n="15"/>αὐτὸς ὁ ναύτης ἀπαντήσῃ 

    <lb n="16"/>πρὸς <choice><corr>χειρογραφίαν</corr><sic>χιρογραφιαν</sic></choice>, οὐκ<g type="mid punctus"/> ὀλίγως 

    <lb n="17"/>γὰρ ἐνοχλούμεθα. ἐὰν δὲ ἀμελή-

    <lb n="18"/>σῃς, ὁ οἶκος ἡμῶν <choice><corr>περιστάσει</corr><sic>περιστασι</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="19"/>κοινωνεῖν μέλλει διὰ τὴν 

    <lb n="20"/>ἀπουσίαν τοῦ γεούχου <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>πὸ τοῦ 

    <lb n="21"/>φορτικοῦ Ἀμμωνίου σπεκουλά-

    <lb n="22"/>τορος καὶ τοῦ ἐπαρχικοῦ. εἴ τι δὲ 

    <lb n="23"/>ἀργύρια ἔχεις παρὰ σοὶ ἢ ὁλο-

    <lb n="24"/>κόττινα, ἐν τάχει <choice><corr><expan>ἀπόστειλο<ex cert="high">ν</ex></expan></corr><sic>αποστιλο</sic></choice>· 

    <lb n="25"/>τοσαύτας τὰρ προσδοχὰς χρε-

    <lb n="26"/>ωστοῦμεν, καὶ οὐκέτι πιστευ-

    <lb n="27"/>όμεθα, ἐὰν μὴ εὐγνωμονή-

    <lb n="28"/>σωμεν. πέμπων δὲ <expan>δήλωσο<ex cert="high">ν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="29"/>τοῖς σοῖς παρασχεῖν μοι τὴν <subst><add place="inline"><expan>ὑπ<ex cert="high">ο</ex></expan>-

    <lb n="30"/>λοιπάδ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear></add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">υπλοιπαδ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">ν</del></del></subst> τοῦ οἴνου καὶ τῆς καθό-

    <lb n="31"/>λου μονάδαν μίαν ἥμισυ <num value="1  1/2 "/>. ὁ 

    <lb n="32"/>ὁλοκόττινος νῦν <expan>μυ<ex cert="high">ριάδων</ex></expan> <num value="2020">Βκ</num> <num value="20200000"/> 

    <lb n="33"/>ἐστίν· κατέβη γάρ. μὴ ἀμελή-

    <lb n="34"/>σῃς ἐν τῇ σήμερον τὸ <expan>πλοῖο<ex cert="high">ν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="35"/>ἢ τὸν ναύτην <choice><corr>ἀποστεῖλαι</corr><sic>αποστιλαι</sic></choice>. ἐρ-

    <lb n="36"/>ρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι 

    <lb n="37"/>πολλοῖς χρόνοις, ἄδελφε. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="38"/>κυρίῳ ἀδελφῷ    Ὡρίωνι Ἑρμεία<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς</supplied>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.21597" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.21597" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date precision="low" type="textDate">ca. 370</date></p></div><div n="meta.21597" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. BL VII, S. 136 und BL VIII, S. 242. Zum Ort (Hermopolites?) vgl. BL XI, S. 148.</p></div><div n="meta.21597" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">9</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1223</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">21597</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">9</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1223</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;9;1223" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.21597" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">242</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume"/>,S. <biblScope type="pages"/></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.21597" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Tyche 11, 1996, Tafel 10</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.21597" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublica